Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:42.53,OP - present,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,420)}Delphi's Fansub uvádí
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:03.37,name,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\pos(527,156)}Překlad:   maggot4
